# ============================================================================
# Production Environment Variables
# ============================================================================
# These variables are used when building for production (npm run build)

# API URL for production (HTTPS required)
# Your deployed backend on Render.com
VITE_API_URL=https://product-search-agent-api.onrender.com

# WebSocket URL for production (WSS - secure WebSocket required)
# Your deployed backend WebSocket endpoint
VITE_WS_URL=wss://product-search-agent-api.onrender.com/ws/notifications

# ============================================================================
# DEPLOYMENT NOTES
# ============================================================================
# Backend URL: https://product-search-agent-api.onrender.com
# Frontend URL: https://product-search-agent-ff7s.onrender.com
# Last Updated: 2026-04-21
# 
# After updating these variables:
# 1. Rebuild frontend: npm run build
# 2. Redeploy to Render (it will auto-deploy if connected to GitHub)
# 3. Update backend CORS_ORIGINS environment variable to include frontend URL